<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Thank you for your booking, <%= @booking.passengers[0].name %></h1>
    <p>
      You have successfully booked your flight, please find details below:
    </p>
    <p>Origin: <%= @booking.flight.origin.name %></p><br>
    <p>Destination: <%= @booking.flight.destination.name %></p><br>
    <p>Date: <%= @booking.flight.date %></p><br>
    <p>
      To find your booking, just follow this link: <%= @url %>.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for chosing to fly with us and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>